{"id": 2678, "genre": 1001, "title": "今年你都达成了哪些“不太好跟别人说，但自己还挺得意”的小成就？", "description": "没啥可跟别人炫耀的，但是自己心里觉得挺满足的一些小事件。（题图来自：iStock ©️ cosmaa）", "record_count": 7259, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181217171906li6IPr1HBfbYQw3E.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-12-20T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 318464, "content": "早起做瘦腿训练……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380082}, {"id": 318209, "content": "长到了大概的人生方向", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537946}, {"id": 317956, "content": "救了一只海鸥", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1517621}, {"id": 317957, "content": "超前完成项目", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512036}, {"id": 317958, "content": "活着", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1523697}, {"id": 318470, "content": "从觉得分手了要死了到把她忘得一干二净只用了一个礼拜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1234480}, {"id": 317959, "content": "走出婚姻阴影", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537260}, {"id": 317961, "content": "考上了理想大学，社交能力比以前好了，更加自信了，也更加开心了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537263}, {"id": 318985, "content": "两个月内将一年都没看完的知识，看了5，6遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541931}, {"id": 317962, "content": "孕36周了只长了11公斤，没有水肿，没有妊娠纹也没有什么不适，老公说我现在就像只青蛙，只有肚子大了😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973739}, {"id": 318219, "content": "跟你去玩耍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537979}, {"id": 317964, "content": "跨过高考这道坎，走出抑郁倾向，变得自信，更会和人相处", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1368740}, {"id": 319244, "content": "考试周室友在宿舍待了一个星期\n我在图书馆待了一个星期", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1522014}, {"id": 317965, "content": "今天我又加班了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537274}, {"id": 317966, "content": "与一家不要女生的单位签了三方，目前备考，考上了就不去工作了。(ಡωಡ)hiahiahia", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537277}, {"id": 319502, "content": "去奥美实习hhh", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427726}, {"id": 317968, "content": "市政二建考试过了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537283}, {"id": 318224, "content": "明确了未来的方向并付诸努力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250367}, {"id": 317969, "content": "戒烟戒酒算吗", "image": "img/option/option/20181220192805XZEUCjHs6Fh4Queq.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537285}, {"id": 318481, "content": "碰到喜欢的人并脱单", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540070}, {"id": 317970, "content": "减肥成功，今年唯一可喜可贺的事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 824231}, {"id": 317971, "content": "鼓足勇气约出了喜欢的女孩", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800043}, {"id": 318484, "content": "付妮妮", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540070}, {"id": 318740, "content": "母胎solo27年，终于脱单破处算吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217909}, {"id": 317973, "content": "考到驾照", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1171732}, {"id": 317974, "content": "尿了一夜血红色的尿 疯狂怀疑自己是痔疮/胃出血 次日清晨爬去医院看病 结果只是因为红心火龙果吃多了 尿出了色素尿 人生一夜之间经历大起大落🙃", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1342954}, {"id": 317975, "content": "管playstation和xbox两大主机平台", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537296}, {"id": 317976, "content": "第一次痛经痛到走不动路😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author"