: 0, "author": 1379219}, {"id": 317993, "content": "nothing", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 318505, "content": "很荣幸的是成为了2000人当中的管理者 当然了是QQ群", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540140}, {"id": 317994, "content": "和17年一样什么都没做 还他tm丢了个女朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1537348}, {"id": 317995, "content": "在街上遇到一个哭诉她前男友还是那么短的女孩并收留了她。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1529934}, {"id": 317996, "content": "跟男神谈恋爱，找到了中意工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221015}, {"id": 323372, "content": "可以坦然接受孤独和面对失望", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1561470}, {"id": 317997, "content": "和男友又在一起一年，没有闹分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 985822}, {"id": 317998, "content": "认清了现实", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1322587}]}